Interface Concept<O,J>

    public interface Concept<O,J>
extends Axiom.Descriptor<O,J>
    This interface is a part of the core of OWLOOP architecture. It contains interfaces of the expressions that can be applied to the OWL entity OWLClass (i.e., OWLClass).

    The expressions are the following:

    • Concept.Equivalent: this expression describes that a Class is equivalent to another Class.
    • Concept.Disjoint: this expression describes that a Class is disjoint to another Class.
    • Concept.Sub: this expression describes that a Class subsumes another Class.
    • Concept.Super: this expression describes that a Class is a super-class of another Class.
    • Concept.Instance: this expression describes an Individual of a Class.
    • Concept.Definition: this expression describes the definition of a Class..
